    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices or assemblies of devices designed to support artillery and heavy small arms such as machine guns. They range from simple tripods to complex supporting, pivoting, and elevating mechanisms on gun carriages.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
